Package sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.services.listeners

Interfaces and reference implementations of core listener service and its components.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ListenerClassesSupplier
    A class that can supply a set of Listener classes.
    ListenerManager
    An object responsible for managing registrations of Listener instances.
    ListenerManagerFactory
    The ListenerManagerFactory creates ListenerManager instances.
    ListenerProvider
    An object responsible for providing Listener instances.
    ListenerProvider.Builder
    A builder for creating listener provider instances.
    ListenerProviderFactory
    The ListenerProviderFactory creates ListenerProvider instances.
    ListenerService
    An object with an operational state providing access to the underlying listener provider and manager.
    ListenerService.Builder
    A builder for creating listener service instances.
    ListenerServiceFactory
    The ListenerServiceFactory creates ListenerService instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractListenerManager
    An abstract implementation of ListenerManager.
    AbstractListenerProvider
    An abstract implementation of ListenerProvider.
    AbstractListenerService
    An abstract implementation of ListenerService.
    AbstractListenerService.AbstractBuilder<B extends AbstractListenerService.AbstractBuilder<B>>
    An abstract builder for creating listener service instances.
    ForwardingListenerManager
    A listener manager which forwards all its method calls to another listener manager.
    ForwardingListenerProvider
    A listener provider which forwards all its method calls to another listener provider.
    ListenerManagers
    Static utility methods pertaining to ListenerManager instances.
    ListenerProviders
    Static utility methods pertaining to ListenerProvider instances.
    ListenerServices
    Static utility methods pertaining to ListenerService instances.
